    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/22456c6f9bf8d478775349e81ec69712.poster.avif?t=1771103848\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/22456c6f9bf8d478775349e81ec69712.webm?t=1771103848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/22456c6f9bf8d478775349e81ec69712.mp4?t=1771103848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/9b081e7a6217958c1ab3d4bfa9db7e82.avif?t=1771103848\" width=616 height=142 /></span><br>这是一场危险的事故，华西丽莎的旅程和她为巴巴亚加提供的服务由一系列玩法多样的迷你游戏组成。<br><br>与华西丽莎和她的娃娃一起，您将走过童话英雄的道路，克服活人世界与死人世界之间的障碍，执行令人毛骨悚然的芭芭雅嘎的任务，向她证明您值得她的青睐，为此您将获得火之力量的礼物。<br><br>沿途你会遇到<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/e2f36d9efecdef7187479b920313fc51.poster.avif?t=1771103848\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/e2f36d9efecdef7187479b920313fc51.webm?t=1771103848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/e2f36d9efecdef7187479b920313fc51.mp4?t=1771103848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>战斗任务<br>• 打小鬼子<br>• 在战斗中打败落水鬼、沼泽领主和林妖<br>• 打败邪恶的继母<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/dfd56e26f897ca5017b4058b679e6b7e.poster.avif?t=1771103848\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/dfd56e26f897ca5017b4058b679e6b7e.webm?t=1771103848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/dfd56e26f897ca5017b4058b679e6b7e.mp4?t=1771103848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>家庭任务<br>• 洗很多碗<br>• 洗衣服 <br>• 清扫农舍<br>• 搋了一块面然后烤大馅饼<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/6a17aad49fe956ff52f9d876b714f754.poster.avif?t=1771103848\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/6a17aad49fe956ff52f9d876b714f754.webm?t=1771103848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/6a17aad49fe956ff52f9d876b714f754.mp4?t=1771103848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>注意力任务<br>• 从雾里找出口<br>• 走出树林<br>• 别迷失在水下草丛中<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/5f709bb14eeb6e89da8386ad24210199.poster.avif?t=1771103848\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/5f709bb14eeb6e89da8386ad24210199.webm?t=1771103848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/5f709bb14eeb6e89da8386ad24210199.mp4?t=1771103848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>敏捷性任务 <br>• 在不撞到熟睡的落水鬼的情况下偷偷溜进去<br>• 悄无声息地通过，让沼泽领主听不见<br>• 避开林妖的视线<br>• 从芭芭雅嘎逃脱<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/4d931fe0a9303d06f9ccb04c2186623e.poster.avif?t=1771103848\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/4d931fe0a9303d06f9ccb04c2186623e.webm?t=1771103848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/4d931fe0a9303d06f9ccb04c2186623e.mp4?t=1771103848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/ef5d7ba1408f3efa280a264fdb571c89.avif?t=1771103848\" width=616 height=142 /></span><br>• 游戏以未经改编的童话故事和童话主题为基础，其中包含在现代文化中可归类为恐怖类型的元素。<br><br>• 讲述人用南俄方言讲述一个故事。您将听到俄罗斯古代村庄里的方言。<br><br>• 根据俄罗斯中部和南部地区民歌改编的原创伴奏音乐。<br><br>• 还有一部关于童话人物和故事、恶魔生物、日常用品、习俗和仪式的综合性百科全书，由一位民俗学家顾问协助编纂。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/5641f10e6782eb2a9bfb570b996f2d2c.avif?t=1771103848\" width=616 height=250 /></span>",
